y:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/static/images/blogImage/20210102011001.jpg\" style=\"height:297px; width:666px\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15px\"><strong>3.选择刚刚创建的组，再次点击右侧的+号，选择第一项开始添加</strong></span></span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/static/images/blogImage/20210102011230.jpg\" style=\"height:298px; width:666px\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15px\"><strong>4.Abbreviation处填关键字（比如我填pi，那么我在敲代码时键入pi时就会出现提示），Description处填提示描述，Template text填自动补全的代码内容</strong></span></span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/static/images/blogImage/20210102011938.jpg\" style=\"height:283px; width:666px\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15px\"><strong>5.选中Java，然后点击OK键即可</strong></span></span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/static/images/blogImage/20210102011607.jpg\" style=\"height:527px; width:666px\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15px\"><strong>6.效果如下</strong></span></span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/static/images/blogImage/20210102012642.jpg\" style=\"height:226px; width:666px\" /></span></span></p>\r\n','2021-01-02 01:26:59',346,5,0,NULL),(79,'GitHub新建仓库','\n1.来到GitHub首页,点击左侧的NEW按钮\n\n\n\n\n\n2.输入名称、描述、选择仓库类型（公开或私有）\n\n\n\n\n\n3.点击最下方的创建按钮即可